            <title>特朗普遭槍擊後，馬斯克第一時間發推力挺</title>
            <description>&lt;div class=&quot;wp-block-image&quot;&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;aligncenter size-full&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.ruancan.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2024071401440814.png&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


